==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: White horse
<hw>White horse</hw>. <def>A large mass of tough sinewy substance in the
head of sperm whales, just above the upper jaw and extending in streaks
into the junk above it. It resembles blubber, but contains no oil. Also,
the part of the head in which it occurs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>White-hot</ent>⟦br⟧
